=======================================================================
Collection - A Simple Collection View

Version 1.0     27 September 2013   Initial version.
=======================================================================

**THIS BUG WAS RESOLVED IN iOS 9.3**

This is a example project to reproduce a bug in the way that iOS 7
repostions popovers when a view is rotated.

For further details see the following blog post:

https://useyourloaf.com/blog/uipopover-arrow-not-repositioned-correctly-on-rotation/

You can also view the bug report on Open Radar at https://openradar.appspot.com/14995477
